.TH VALTHON 1
.SH NAME
py2vln \- Translate python files to valthon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B py2vln
[\fIFLAGS\fR]
.IR scriptfile
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B py2vln
is a program that translates regular python scripts to valthon
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version number and exit.
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-output
Specify the name of output file.
